"To use it, select :guilabel:`Google Place Map` and enter your :ref:`API Key "
"<address_autocomplete/generate_api_key>`."
msgstr ""
"כדי להשתמש בו, בחר :guilabel:`Google Place Map` והזן את :ref:`מפתח ה-API "
"<address_autocomplete/generate_api_key>` שלך."

